org.melior.client.kafka

Class SSLEngineFactory

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.melior.client.kafka.SSLEngineFactory
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Closeable, AutoCloseable, org.apache.kafka.common.Configurable, org.apache.kafka.common.security.auth.SslEngineFactory

    public final class SSLEngineFactory
extends Object
implements org.apache.kafka.common.security.auth.SslEngineFactory
    Instantiates an SSLEngine for use in Kafka clients that establish secure connections to Kafka servers. The SSLContext from which the SSLEngine is created can either be fully trusting or will require a concrete key store and/or a concrete trust store that is referenced in the remoting client configuration.
    Since:
    2.3
    Author:
    Melior
